Package streamprocessor

Record Class Processor

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
streamprocessor.Processor
Record Components:
line - the original complete line
payLoad - after the tag and instruction
transformation - the transformation to be effective for the current line
instruction - the instruction word found in the line
lineNumber - sic
text - the text before the comment and tag
indent - the indentation to apply
startEnd - '', 'start' or 'end'
All Implemented Interfaces:
Function<Processor,Stream<String>>
public record Processor(String line, String payLoad, Function<Processor,Stream<String>> transformation, String instruction, int lineNumber, String text, String indent, String startEnd) extends Record implements Function<Processor,Stream<String>>
Box that processes its content with a given function into a Stream of Strings.
Author:
Pieter van den Hombergh <pieter.van.den.hombergh@gmail.com>
